ination with other agents that are potentially hepatotoxic (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/94724/', '', 'Lamivudine, Paritaprevir, Glecaprevir, Tenofovir alafenamide, Maraviroc, Amprenavir, Simeprevir, Valaciclovir, Zanamivir, Cabotegravir, Lenacapavir, More', 'Vitamin A, Chloramphenicol, Fluorometholone, Azelaic acid, Adapalene, Tetracycline, Oxytetracycline, Omadacycline, Eravacycline, Demeclocycline, Sarecycline, More', 1767369485);
